  <brief_title>A Randomized Controlled Study Comparing Priming Solution Containing Crystalloid or Packed Red Blood Cells in Patients Treated With Isolated Limb Perfusion.</brief_title>
  <acronym>ILP-Prime</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Study With the Aim to Compare Crystalloid Prime Solution With a Prime Solution Containing Packed Red Blood Cells in Relation to the Patient's Regional Metabolic Needs and Immunological Influence During Isolated Limb Perfusion</official_title>
  <sponsors>
